  "number": 339,
  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/339",
  "title": "Switch to using uber/npm-shrinkwrap",
  "body": "npm shrinkwrap is broken in many ways, [uber/npm-shrinkwrap](https://github.com/uber/npm-shrinkwrap) seems: promising, well maintained\n\nLet's give it a try.\n\nTODO:\n- [ ] use uber/npm-shrinkwrap to regenerate our shrinkwrap\n- [ ] read the available options\n- [ ] modify CONTRIBUTING guide to indicate how to upgrade/remove a package and redoing the shrinkwrap\n\nIf this works that's great because we can then switch to npm@3 without worrying about shrinkwrap.\n",
